Hey all.  Thought I might share a funny thing that could have been bad.

I started my bus up this afternoon and ran inside to grab something letting
her idle a bit.  When I came back out.........my bus was GONE!
stolen?.......nope.  Seems that I need to pay a little attention to my
Ebrake

